    <text>
        <body>
            <pb n="1R"/>
            <p rend="align(right)"><placeName>San-Francisco</placeName>
                <date>October the 31st./1862</date>.</p>
            <p rend="align(right)">My Rev: Friend <addressee>Leeser</addressee>!</p>
            <p>Long has it been my duty to write to you informing you<lb/> of my dear Husband,
                children and my constant good<lb/> health and happiness hoping the same is with
                you,<lb/> which is <sic>allway's</sic> the greatest blessing, I have written<lb/>
                one letter since I have been here, but received no answer<lb/> no doubt you have
                never received it, I hope you will<lb/> please me with a letter as it will please me
                very much.<lb/> I make good use of the Prayer book and take it to your<lb/>
                Synagogue, I have often spoken about you to our<lb/>
                <persName>Rev. E. Hohn</persName> he is a fine man and is liked very<lb/> much, I
                wish you could see what a nice Synagogue<lb/> we have here, I will send you one of
                my <sic>card's</sic> hoping<lb/> you will return the compliment, I can also inform
                you<lb/> the best of my dear brother <persName>David</persName> and his family, little<lb/>
                <persName>Moses</persName> will be Ber<add>?</add>it<add>?</add>ag tomorrow, they do
                not live<lb/> in the City they live in <placeName>San-Jose</placeName> which is 50
                miles<lb/> from here, I hope you will excuse me for my poor<lb/> writing as my
                little boy 11 <sic>month's</sic> old who wishes to have<lb/> his hand in it, and my
                oldest a boy 3 Â½ year old</p>
            <pb n="1V"/>
            <p>I must say myself that they are fine <sic>boy's</sic>,<lb/> My dear Husband
                    <sic>send's</sic> his best <sic>regard's</sic> to you.<lb/> I hope you will
                visit Father <sic>occasionaly</sic>.</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">I remain your sincere friend.</p>
            <p rend="indent(2)"><persName role="author">Isabella Meyerfeld</persName>.</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">P. S. My dear Sister in law tells me she is<lb/> acquainted with you
                therefore I need not introduce<lb/> you. <persName role="author">I.
                    Meyerfeld</persName>.</p>
        </body>
